parameters:
It seems to be a door leading to the 5th floor, but no matter how much
I push or pull, it won't budge. It appears to be locked.

When I inserted the key I obtained from the safe into the keyhole, the
lock easily opened. The door, although rusty, also opened easily.

......Am I being lured in? Or perhaps, is this the nature of the other
world? Does this other world recognize someone as insignificant as
myself?
お――――ん。って感じで普通の移動ではない感じ

It felt like the door opened, perhaps because of Araka's power...
Ignoring the thought of go back. If Araka were to see it, she would
surely be furious like a raging fire. To make her angry, I will open
the door.

When I approached out of curiosity, I found something like a jewel
lying there. It seemed to be one of the beads that were probably
connected as a rosary.
ex汚染のヤツ、主人公、なんか拾う

As I was walking, I suddenly smelled something sweet. It wasn't a
rotten sweetness, but rather somewhere refreshing.

I thought my nose had become foolishly accustomed to the smell of
mold, but it seems that I can still recognize it to some extent. This
is the smell of Araka.

When I looked around, there was something sparkling. Could this be...
a piece of a glass marble or something?
Will you pick up the fragment?

When I picked it up, the smell faded. Or perhaps there was
no smell to begin with.

......I couldn't perceive any visuals or anything. Only Araka's
heart was conveyed to me.
